  <lastupdated>2014-02-24</lastupdated>
  <definitions>
    <item>
      <id>1</id>
      <text>A molecular entity or chemical species capable of donating a hydron (proton) (see Brønsted acid) or capable of forming a covalent bond with an electron pair (see Lewis acid).</text>
